aVSo we'd racked up at this stage about 600,000 dollars
p147
aVworth of debt. So if Movember 2006 didn't happen,
p148
aVthe four founders, well, we would've been broke,
p149
aVwe would've been homeless, sitting on the street
p150
aVwith mustaches. (Laughter)
p151
aVBut we thought, you know what, if that's the worst thing
p152
aVthat happens, so what?
p153
aVWe're going to have a lot of fun doing it, and it taught us
p154
aVthe importance of taking risks and really smart risks.
