aa(lp189
VSo in 2007, we brought the campaign across here,
p190
aVand it was, it set the stage for the campaign.
p191
aVIt wasn't as successful as we thought it would be.
p192
aVWe were sort of very gung ho with our success in Australia
p193
aVand New Zealand at that stage.
